%% Simplified cross-account access flow diagram
%% Shows the step-by-step authentication and authorization process

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant DevUser as Dev IAM User<br/>(pulldb-dev-user)
    participant LocalProfile as Local AWS Profile<br/>(pr-prod-cross-account)
    participant STS as AWS STS Service
    participant ProdRole as Prod IAM Role<br/>(cross-account-read-role)
    participant S3 as Prod S3 Bucket
    participant KMS as KMS Key
    participant SSM as Parameter Store
    participant pullDB as pullDB Application

    Note over DevUser,LocalProfile: Development/Staging Account (345321506926 / 333204494849)
    Note over ProdRole,SSM: Production Account (448509429610)
    
    pullDB->>LocalProfile: Load AWS_PROFILE=pr-prod-cross-account
    LocalProfile->>LocalProfile: Read source_profile (pr-dev)<br/>Read role_arn<br/>Read external_id
    
    LocalProfile->>DevUser: Get base credentials<br/>(Access Key + Secret)
    DevUser-->>LocalProfile: Return credentials
    
    LocalProfile->>STS: AssumeRole Request<br/>role_arn + external_id
    
    Note over STS: Validate Request
    STS->>ProdRole: Check trust policy
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify principal = dev account
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify external_id matches
    ProdRole-->>STS: Trust policy valid
    
    STS->>STS: Generate temporary credentials<br/>(AccessKeyId, SecretAccessKey, SessionToken)<br/>Valid for max_session_duration
    
    STS-->>LocalProfile: Return temporary credentials
    LocalProfile-->>pullDB: Credentials ready
    
    Note over pullDB: Configuration Loading
    pullDB->>SSM: GetParameter(/pulldb/prod/mysql/host)
    SSM->>ProdRole: Check permissions
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify ssm:GetParameter allowed
    ProdRole-->>SSM: Permission granted
    SSM->>KMS: Decrypt SecureString
    KMS->>ProdRole: Check kms:Decrypt permission
    ProdRole-->>KMS: Permission granted (via SSM)
    KMS-->>SSM: Decrypted value
    SSM-->>pullDB: MySQL host value
    
    pullDB->>SSM: GetParameter(/pulldb/prod/mysql/password)
    SSM->>SSM: Check permissions (cached)
    SSM->>KMS: Decrypt SecureString
    KMS-->>SSM: Decrypted value
    SSM-->>pullDB: MySQL password value
    
    Note over pullDB: Restore Workflow
    pullDB->>S3: ListObjectsV2(daily/prod/customer123/)
    S3->>ProdRole: Check permissions
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify s3:ListBucket allowed
    ProdRole-->>S3: Permission granted
    S3-->>pullDB: List of backup files
    
    pullDB->>S3: GetObject(latest_backup.tar)
    S3->>ProdRole: Check permissions
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify s3:GetObject allowed
    ProdRole->>ProdRole: Verify s3:PutObject DENIED
    ProdRole-->>S3: Get permission granted
    S3->>KMS: Decrypt object (SSE-KMS)
    KMS->>ProdRole: Check kms:Decrypt permission
    ProdRole-->>KMS: Permission granted (via S3)
    KMS-->>S3: Decrypted data stream
    S3-->>pullDB: Backup file stream
    
    Note over pullDB: Credentials Auto-Refresh
    pullDB->>LocalProfile: Need credentials (after TTL)
    LocalProfile->>STS: AssumeRole (automatic refresh)
    STS-->>LocalProfile: New temporary credentials
    LocalProfile-->>pullDB: Refreshed credentials
    
    Note over DevUser,SSM: Audit Trail
    STS-->>STS: Log AssumeRole event to CloudTrail
    S3-->>S3: Log data access to CloudTrail
    SSM-->>SSM: Log parameter access to CloudTrail
